<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-1628] RedHat init script status is a no-op</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1628</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current bare-bones init script is a little too bare-bones. The &quot;status&quot; argument make a successful no-op, which can be pretty misleading.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;RedHat-like Linux&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12477654">CASSANDRA-1628</key>
