                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12922160" author="addumb" created="Mon, 18 Oct 2010 17:38:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do a pretty minimal status check.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12922183" author="addumb" created="Mon, 18 Oct 2010 18:03:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also include the status option in the Usage section.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12922194" author="zznate" created="Mon, 18 Oct 2010 18:14:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Works as advertised: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/etc/init.d/cassandra status&lt;br/&gt;
cassandra (pid  1101) is running...&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;After shutdown:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/etc/init.d/cassandra status&lt;br/&gt;
cassandra is stopped&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12922376" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 19 Oct 2010 00:10:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12922565" author="hudson" created="Tue, 19 Oct 2010 14:15:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra #570 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/570/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/570/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    Redhat init script prints the status when asked.  Patch by Adam Gray, reviewed by brandonwilliams for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1628&quot; title=&quot;RedHat init script status is a no-op&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-1628&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-1628&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
